<emphasis box="[151,242,1406,1431]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="61">Biology</emphasis>
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="10.[151,1436,1406,1552]" pageId="10" pageNumber="61">The species of the genus usually live in tussock grass under subtropical bushes and broad-leaf trees which grow in the wet and half-shady zone at medium elevation in southwestern Yunnan. The food plant has been unknown in field.</paragraph>
